title: Zack Snyder's Justice League - Movie Review
author: Chris Stuckmann
description: Chris Stuckmann reviews Zack Snyder's Justice League, starring Henry Cavill, Ben Affleck, Gal Gadot, Amy Adams, Ray Fisher, Jared Leto, Jason Momoa, Ezra Miller, Willem Dafoe, Jesse Eisenberg, Jeremy Irons, Connie Nielsen, J.K. Simmons, Ciarán Hinds. Directed by Zack Snyder.
